Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Grants you a 40' radius aura which increases your Henchmen's AoE Defense by 10% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This enhancement can only be slotted in a Mastermind pet power.
DisplayName: Attuned Command of the Mastermind F
